latestPosts.caption: Laut ke buddhu ghar ko aaye! I love food - love cooking, love eating, love thinking about it. But for a few years I was trying to be fitter but missing the pure joy food gives me. And that’s when I read the two books by Rujuta Diwekar - realised ghar ka khana, season ka khana, fresh khana, enjoy karke khana, mindfully khana - the simpler habits made all the difference. Now I feel I’m at my fittest in the last ten years, but I’m still the biggest foodie. I watch new recipes, cook new things, stay excited for all my meals. Thanks @rujuta.diwekar for making me fall in love with ghar ka khana ♥️
